data.description: Step inside this charming, single family home in the  gated community of Roosevelt Park in Avondale.  Built in 2021, this 2-story home features an open kitchen with a large island, a generously sized family room and half bath on the first floor.  On the second floor, you'll discover 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a spacious loft.  The backyard boasts an extended paver patio and recently installed artificial turf making it low-maintenance and perfect for enjoying the beautiful Arizona weather.  Roosevelt Park also offers a  community pool, multiple parks, basketball courts and walking/biking trails throughout. Located near Loop 101 and the I-10 you'll have easy access to freeways, shopping and entertainment.
